# Task 1 – Business Objectives

## Project

**Virtual Agent–Driven SLA Breach Awareness & Justification System**

---

## Objective

This task defines the primary business objectives of the project. The focus is on improving Service Level Agreement (SLA) governance by using ServiceNow Administration features such as Virtual Agent, Flow Designer, UI Policies, and Reporting.

---

## Business Goals

* Proactive SLA Awareness
* Reduce SLA Violations
* Improve SLA Governance
* Enhance User Experience
* Strengthen Accountability
* Operational Transparency

---

## Deliverables

* Business Objectives Documentation
* Functional Business Goals
* Expected Outcomes
* Project Overview

---

## Technologies Used

* ServiceNow Administration
* Virtual Agent
* SLA Management
* Flow Designer
* UI Policies
* Reports & Dashboards

---

## Expected Outcome

The project establishes a proactive SLA management process that minimizes SLA breaches, improves accountability, enhances user experience, and provides management with clear visibility into SLA performance through reports and dashboards.

---

**Status:** Completed

**Internship:** SmartBridge ServiceNow Administration

**Task:** 1 – Business Objectives

